      "content": "it’s weird that you say that... like you actually get it. everyone else makes me feel like i'm just being dramatic, but it really does feel like the \"me\" part of me is already gone. if the essence is gone, what am i even doing here? what is the purpose of the vessel if the soul isn't in it anymore?",
